Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) hybrid electric jet engines without turbines in which compressors are powered by fuel cells instead of the turbines are promising and developmental aero-engines for unmanned aerial vehicles.
Titulo: Determination of the safe operation zone for a turbine-less and solid oxide fuel cell hybrid electric jet engine on unmanned aerial vehicles

Sentencas: The hybrid electric jet engine combines the merits of turbo-electric engines and fuel cell engines.
Titulo: Determination of the safe operation zone for a turbine-less and solid oxide fuel cell hybrid electric jet engine on unmanned aerial vehicles

Sentencas: To avoid component malfunctions and engine performance deterioration, the determination of the safe operation zone is necessary.
Titulo: Determination of the safe operation zone for a turbine-less and solid oxide fuel cell hybrid electric jet engine on unmanned aerial vehicles

Sentencas: In this study, a performance analysis model of the hybrid electric jet engine is built and the main conclusions are as follows.
Titulo: Determination of the safe operation zone for a turbine-less and solid oxide fuel cell hybrid electric jet engine on unmanned aerial vehicles

Sentencas: The safe operating zone of the hybrid engine is not restricted by turbine inlet temperature.
Titulo: Determination of the safe operation zone for a turbine-less and solid oxide fuel cell hybrid electric jet engine on unmanned aerial vehicles

Sentencas: Under low fuel flow rate and low air flow rate, zones of too low reforming temperature or too low SOFC open voltage exist.
Titulo: Determination of the safe operation zone for a turbine-less and solid oxide fuel cell hybrid electric jet engine on unmanned aerial vehicles

Sentencas: An unbalanced energy zone exists under high fuel flow rate and low air flow rate.
Titulo: Determination of the safe operation zone for a turbine-less and solid oxide fuel cell hybrid electric jet engine on unmanned aerial vehicles

Sentencas: The power produced by the SOFC is above that consumed by the compressor.
Titulo: Determination of the safe operation zone for a turbine-less and solid oxide fuel cell hybrid electric jet engine on unmanned aerial vehicles

Sentencas: The lower boundary of the safe zone is determined by the choke zone of the compressors.
Titulo: Determination of the safe operation zone for a turbine-less and solid oxide fuel cell hybrid electric jet engine on unmanned aerial vehicles

Sentencas: In the safe zone, the hybrid engine has properties of high specific thrust (837.6 N/ (kg.s(-1))) and high thermal efficiency (70.4%) at high fuel low and air flow rate.
